---
By: Lakshmana Sarma
Locus:
  Page: 119
  Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Ego
---
The ego is simply the ignorance that limits the real Self to a single body
out of a multitude of bodies, all of which are its own creation. ...We need
to realize in all its implications the fact that the ego itself is the
source of all the evil that besets life.
